<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Relieving and Experience Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Calibri', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12pt;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            width: 210mm; /* A4 width */
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .date {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .paragraph {
            margin: 0 0 30pt 0;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 40pt;
        }
        .note {
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-top: 20pt;
        }
        .sincere-line {
            margin-top: 25pt;
            margin-bottom: 2pt;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .for-company-line {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Letterhead can be included here if needed -->
        <p class="date"><%= relieving_date %></p>
        <p class="title">Relieving and Experience Letter</p>
        <p class="paragraph">Employee Name: <%= employee_name %></p>
        <% if (employee_id) { %>
            <p class="paragraph">Employee ID: <%= employee_id %></p>
        <% } %>
        <p class="paragraph">This is with regard to your resignation,</p>
        <p class="paragraph">
            Dated <%= resignation_date %> from the position of <strong><%= designation %></strong> - We would like to inform you that you have been relieved of your duties at the end of business hours of <%= relieving_date %>.
        </p>
        <p class="paragraph">
            We enjoyed working with you and thank you for the service rendered from <strong><%= start_date %></strong> to <strong><%= relieving_date %></strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="paragraph">We wish you good luck for future endeavours.</p>
        <p class="sincere-line">Yours sincerely,</p>
        <p class="for-company-line">For Amazon IT Solutions</p>
        <% if (signaturePath) { %>
  <div style="margin-top: 5mm;">
    <img src="<%= signaturePath %>" alt="Authorized Signature" style="width:90px; height:auto; opacity:0.95;" />
  </div>
<% } %>

        <p class="signature"><%= hrName %></p>
        <p class="paragraph" style="font-weight: bold;"><%= hrDesignation %></p>
        <p class="note">Note: This is a computer-generated document. No Signature is required*</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>